<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DVNA-PFE — Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<main class="main-content">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="page-title">Dashboard</div>
        <div class="page-subtitle">Connecte en tant que <strong><%= user.username %></strong> — Role : <%= user.role %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="alert alert-warn">
      Cette application contient des vulnerabilites intentionnelles a des fins de demonstration DevSecOps.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); font-weight:500; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:12px;">
    Modules de demonstration
  </div>

  <div class="vuln-grid">

    <a href="/ping" class="vuln-card">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-01</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Ping Tool</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">SonarQube / Semgrep — SAST</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">Command Injection via child_process.exec() avec entree non filtree.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/search" class="vuln-card">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-02</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Recherche utilisateur</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">OWASP ZAP — DAST</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">XSS reflechi — la saisie est affichee sans echappement HTML.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/notes" class="vuln-card">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-03</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Notes privees</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">OWASP ZAP — DAST</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">IDOR — acces aux notes d'autres utilisateurs via manipulation d'ID.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/deserialize" class="vuln-card">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-04</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Deserialisation</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">npm audit / Dep-Check — SCA</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">node-serialize 0.0.4 — CVE permettant une execution de code a distance.</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/xml" class="vuln-card">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-05</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">Parser XML</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">SonarQube / Semgrep — SAST</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">XXE — entites XML externes permettant la lecture de fichiers locaux.</div>
    </a>

    <div class="vuln-card" style="opacity:.6; cursor:default;">
      <div class="vuln-card-num">VULN-06</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-title">En-tetes HTTP</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-tool">OWASP ZAP — DAST</div>
      <div class="vuln-card-desc">X-Frame-Options, CSP, HSTS absents — detectes sur toutes les pages.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>